sequenceDiagram
    participant Node
    participant Gateway
    Node->>Gateway: Uplink (TX)
    Note over Node: Wait 1s (RECEIVE_DELAY1)
    Gateway-->>Node: Downlink (RX1 Window)
    Note over Node: Wait 2s (RECEIVE_DELAY2)
    Gateway-->>Node: Downlink (RX2 Window)
    Note over Node: Sleep (Deep Sleep)
